{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "拉托妮 第4话 少女与罪",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "发生了非常可怕的事。\\n我体内的某些东西正在失去控制。\\n啊啊，神啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "神啊，救救我吧！我的神啊！\\n为什么我会……\\n难道我活在世上就是罪吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "谢谢你能告诉我……\\n这下终于能够\\n理清事件的脉络了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "最初是拉托妮养的黑猫死了。\\n然后野猫们也\\n一个接一个地死去……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "之后开始有人丧命。\\n而你认为那是自己做的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110349_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉托妮",
            "context": "因为……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110349_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉托妮",
            "context": "我在梦里很清楚地看到了……\\n另一个我在做坏事的情景。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110349_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉托妮",
            "context": "我……掐着……\\n猫的脖子……还有人的脖子……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "可是……尸体上留下的手印\\n是成年人的大小。\\n也就是说，不可能是你。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110349_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉托妮",
            "context": "就算这样……也是我。\\n如果不是，\\n我的梦……又是怎么回事？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110349_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉托妮",
            "context": "不要……再来管我了。\\n我会告诉你，你想知道的事。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "诶？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110349_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉托妮",
            "context": "你是来找异端的吧？\\n我知道……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "你说什么！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110349_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉托妮",
            "context": "我在很多人家里\\n吃过饭。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110349_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉托妮",
            "context": "经常……被骂……\\n因为吃饭前忘了向伊莉雅大人祈祷……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110349_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉托妮",
            "context": "但是也有人不会生气……\\n他们会做我很熟悉的祈祷。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "你很熟悉的……也就是说，\\n跟赫希伍德村一样吗！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110349_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉托妮",
            "context": "嗯……我杀掉的老奶奶，\\n还有那个叔叔都是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "原来如此……\\n被盯上的都是异端吗……\\n杀人灭口？还是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110349_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉托妮",
            "context": "库格尔？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "大功一件啊，拉托妮。\\n这下说不定就能\\n洗清你的嫌疑了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110349_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉托妮",
            "context": "诶？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "所以今天就好好休息吧。\\n别担心，我会一直陪着你的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110349_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉托妮",
            "context": "……\\n谢谢你……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村里的女子",
            "context": "啊啊……\\n果然您就是“主”的使者。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村里的女子",
            "context": "我听父亲说了。\\n父亲他……\\n他顺利到达“主”身边了吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110349_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉托妮？",
            "context": "麓可望山脊而不见峻岭。\\n魂渡彼岸方可见之。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村里的女子",
            "context": "啊啊、啊啊！那么请把我也带走，\\n参加“主”的盛宴吧。那样一来\\n我一定可以理解一切，一切的一切！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110349_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉托妮？",
            "context": "汝乃吾掌中之泡影。\\n汝乃吾掌所折之花。\\n若汝渴于禁忌之宴……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110349_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉托妮？",
            "context": "便成全汝。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "唔……唔唔？啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "我……睡着了吗！？\\n不对……我记得昨晚\\n突然两眼一黑……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "对了，拉托妮呢！\\n不、不见了……\\n呃，拉托妮到底去哪了！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "嗯？这是……信？\\n难道……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村里的大妈",
            "context": "在哪！那小姑娘在哪！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村里的大妈",
            "context": "我说！那小姑娘！\\n那个怪物到底在哪啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "喂、喂……突然间怎么了？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村里的大妈",
            "context": "别躲了快出来！\\n不止我家丈夫，连女儿也……\\n不可饶恕！不可饶恕！不可饶恕！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "等、等等。女儿？你女儿？\\n难道昨晚……被杀了吗！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120021_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村长",
            "context": "没错。不止孩子他爸，连女儿也被杀了。\\n异端审问官大人，\\n即使有你在也还是发生了悲剧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120021_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村长",
            "context": "至今为止的一切都是因为\\n我们村收留了那个异端小姑娘。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "如果是这件事……\\n那似乎如你们所愿了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120021_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村长",
            "context": "你说……什么？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "看这个，这是拉托妮留下的字条。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "我不想再给大家造成困扰。\\n我要去一个\\n不会给任何人添麻烦的地方。\\n对不起。永别了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "这下你们满意了！？村长！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "听好了，对于这个村子的\\n异端调查还没有结束。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "你们就好好祈祷拉托妮平安无事吧。\\n她要是有个三长两短，\\n等待你们的调查可没那么简单！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "拉托妮……你可千万别做傻事啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110349_01_03_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}